<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Inquiry Received</title>
    
        <style>
          body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
          }
    
          .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 20px auto;
          }
    
          .header {
            background-color: #4e5ba6;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
          }
    
          .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
          }
    
          .content {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
          }
    
          .content h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
          }
    
          .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
          }
    
          .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            border-collapse: collapse;
          }
    
          .details-table th,
          .details-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            text-align: left;
          }
    
          .details-table th {
            background-color: #4e5ba6;
            color: white;
          }
    
          .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
          }
    
          .footer a {
            color: #ff3399;
            text-decoration: none;
          }
    
          .contact {
            margin-top: 20px;
          }
    
          .contact p {
            margin: 5px 0;
          }
    
          .contact a {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
          }
    
          .contact a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
          }
        </style>
      </head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://mydevpartner.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/uploads/logo.png" alt="Company Logo" />
            <h1>Inquiry Received</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>New Inquiry from Website Visitor</h1>
            <p>A visitor has submitted an inquiry on your website. Below are the details:</p>
            <table class="details-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Details</th>
                        <th>Information</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Full Name:</strong></td>
                        <td><%= fullName %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Email Address:</strong></td>
                        <td><%= emailAddress %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Phone Number:</strong></td>
                        <td><%= phoneNumber %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Subject:</strong></td>
                        <td><%= subject %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Message:</strong></td>
                        <td><%= message %></td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <div class="contact">
                <p>If you need to reply or require more information, you can reach out directly to the visitor at:</p>
                <a style="text-decoration: underline;" href="mailto:hr@gohashinclude.com">Contact the HR team</a>.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>GOHASHINCLUDE</p>
            <p>Nirman Nagar E, P.No.-31 1st Floor, Shree Krishna Tower, Ajmer Rd, opp. Asopa Hospital, Jaipur, Rajasthan 302024</p>
            <p>Copyright Â© GOHASHINCLUDE. All Rights Reserved</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
